What it says on the tin: a tray icon, for xmms2. Nothing more, nothing less (roughly).

Grab the source: [http://code.jollybox.de/pub/xmms2tray/xmms2tray-0.5.1.tar.gz version 0.5.1] / [http://code.jollybox.de/hg/xmms2tray mercurial]

Dependencies:
* Python 2
* PyGTK

Optional Libraries:
* notify-python for notifications bubbles.
* Python Imaging Library PIL if you have cover art and you want to see it in bubbles.